nodes.text: The Quellor sector was a sector in the Colonies region of the galaxy. It contained the Cato Neimoidia system, location of the Neimoidian colony world Cato Neimoidia. During the Clone Wars, the Galactic Republic and the Confederacy of Independent Systems fought on multiple occasions for control of the planet including the defense of Cato Neimoidia and the Battle of Cato Neimoidia.
The Quellor sector was first named in the reference book Ultimate Star Wars, which was released in 2015.
